query:
SELECT sci.productSku, sci.productName, sci.expectedQuantity, sci.checkedQuantity, sci.divergence
FROM stageChecks sc
JOIN stageCheckItems sci ON sc.id = sci.stageCheckId
WHERE sc.customerOrderNumber = 'PED-005'
ORDER BY sci.productSku;
